#: ../../source/language/javascript/prototype.rst:2
msgid "原型链"
msgstr "Prototype Chain"

#: ../../source/language/javascript/prototype.rst:5
msgid "显式原型和隐式原型"
msgstr "Explicit and Implicit Prototypes"

#: ../../source/language/javascript/prototype.rst:6
msgid ""
"JavaScript的原型分为显式原型（explicit prototype property）和隐式原型（implicit prototype "
"link）。"
msgstr "JavaScript prototypes are divided into explicit prototype properties and implicit prototype links."

#: ../../source/language/javascript/prototype.rst:8
msgid "其中显式原型指prototype，是函数的一个属性，这个属性是一个指针，指向一个对象，显示修改对象的原型的属性，只有函数才有该属性"
msgstr "The explicit prototype refers to prototype. It is a property of a function, and this property is a pointer to an object. It explicitly modifies the object's prototype properties. Only functions have this property."

#: ../../source/language/javascript/prototype.rst:10
msgid ""
"隐式原型指JavaScript中任意对象都有的内置属性prototype。在ES5之前没有标准的方法访问这个内置属性，但是大多数浏览器都支持通过 "
"``__proto__`` 来访问。ES5中有了对于这个内置属性标准的Get方法 ``Object.getPrototypeOf()`` 。"
msgstr "The implicit prototype refers to the built-in prototype property that every JavaScript object has. Before ES5, there was no standard method for accessing this built-in property, but most browsers supported access through ``__proto__``. ES5 introduced the standard Get method for this built-in property: ``Object.getPrototypeOf()``."

#: ../../source/language/javascript/prototype.rst:12
msgid ""
"隐式原型指向创建这个对象的函数(constructor)的prototype， ``__proto__`` "
"指向的是当前对象的原型对象，而prototype指向的，是以当前函数作为构造函数构造出来的对象的原型对象。"
msgstr "The implicit prototype points to the prototype of the function (constructor) that created the object. ``__proto__`` points to the current object's prototype object, while prototype points to the prototype object of objects constructed with the current function as the constructor."

#: ../../source/language/javascript/prototype.rst:14
msgid ""
"显式原型的作用用来实现基于原型的继承与属性的共享。 "
"隐式原型的用于构成原型链，同样用于实现基于原型的继承。举个例子，当我们访问obj这个对象中的x属性时，如果在obj中找不到，那么就会沿着 "
"``__proto__`` 依次查找。"
msgstr "The explicit prototype is used to implement prototype-based inheritance and property sharing. The implicit prototype is used to form the prototype chain and also supports prototype-based inheritance. For example, when accessing the x property on an object obj, if it cannot be found on obj, JavaScript searches along ``__proto__`` in sequence."

#: ../../source/language/javascript/prototype.rst:22
msgid "new 的过程"
msgstr "The Process of new"

#: ../../source/language/javascript/prototype.rst:29
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"new的过程拆分成以下三步： - ``var p={};`` 初始化一个对象p - ``p.__proto__ = "
"Person.prototype;`` - ``Person.call(p);`` 构造p，也可以称之为初始化p"
msgstr "The process of new can be split into the following three steps: - ``var p={};`` initializes an object p - ``p.__proto__ = Person.prototype;`` - ``Person.call(p);`` constructs p, which can also be called initializing p"

#: ../../source/language/javascript/prototype.rst:34
msgid "关键在于第二步，我们来证明一下："
msgstr "The key is the second step. This can be demonstrated as follows:"

#: ../../source/language/javascript/prototype.rst:42
msgid "这段代码会返回true。说明我们步骤2是正确的。"
msgstr "This code returns true, showing that step 2 is correct."

#: ../../source/language/javascript/prototype.rst:45
msgid "示例"
msgstr "Example"

#: ../../source/language/javascript/prototype.rst:58
msgid "p是一个引用指向Person的对象。我们在Person的原型上定义了一个sayName方法和age属性，当我们执行p.age时，会先在this的内部查找（也就是构造函数内部），如果没有找到然后再沿着原型链向上追溯。"
msgstr "p is a reference to a Person object. We define a sayName method and an age property on Person's prototype. When p.age is evaluated, JavaScript first looks inside this, that is, inside the constructor. If it is not found, JavaScript then walks up the prototype chain."

#: ../../source/language/javascript/prototype.rst:60
msgid ""
"这里的向上追溯是怎么向上的呢？这里就要使用 ``__proto__`` "
"属性来链接到原型（也就是Person.prototype）进行查找。最终在原型上找到了age属性。"
msgstr "How does this upward lookup happen? The ``__proto__`` property is used to link to the prototype, namely Person.prototype, and perform the lookup. The age property is eventually found on the prototype."

#: ../../source/language/javascript/prototype.rst:63
msgid "原型链污染"
msgstr "Prototype Pollution"

#: ../../source/language/javascript/prototype.rst:64
msgid ""
"如前文提到的，JavaScript是动态继承，通过 ``__proto__`` "
"修改自身对象时会影响到有相同原型的对象。因此当键值对是用户可控的情况下，就可能出现原型链污染。"
msgstr "As mentioned earlier, JavaScript uses dynamic inheritance. Modifying an object through ``__proto__`` affects objects with the same prototype. Therefore, when key-value pairs are user controllable, prototype pollution may occur."
